fields.title: Gear Shifts and Data Rifts Formula 1 Driver Prowess
fields.abstract: Deepened the understanding of the factors influencing driver performance in Formula 1 (F1) racing could provide meaningful insights to improve results on the racetrack.

fields.title: Insight into the Effects of a Peer Math Assistant on Student Academic Performance
fields.abstract: This project takes data collected from the Math Achievement Program (MAP) and pairs it with student grade data to find impactful results regarding how a Peer Math Assistant (PMA) can affect student academic performance
